<http://purl.org/gc/hasBasisSet> rdfs:comment "A property that allows Basis Sets to be assigned to a given quantum methodology"@en ,
                                              "A property that allows to define Basis Set -  finite set of functions used to approximately express the Molecular Orbital wavefunction(s) of system, normally atom centered, consisting of AOs differing in local angular momentum for each atom."@en ;
                                 rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://chemicalsemantics.com/> ;
                                 rdfs:label "has basis set"@en .


